- [x] Fix endless loading bug in [AvailableSlotsScreen](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/scheduling/screens/available_slots_screen.dart#12-36) for today's date by wrapping the initial load in a post-frame callback.
- [x] Update Date Slider in `AppointmentListScreen` to generate a 31-day window strictly centered around the selected date's yesterday, and dynamically rebuild and animate the scroll position when a new calendar date is picked.
- [x] Expand [CreateAppointmentScreen](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/screens/create_appointment_screen.dart#15-24) and `appointment_provider` to embed the full patient details form (DOB, Address, Emergency Contact, Allergies) natively into the Walk-In appointment booking flow, completely eliminating the need for a secondary registration step.

